query:
SELECT
                        t.*
                    FROM
                        tasks t
                        JOIN assignments a ON
                            a.task_id = t.id
                    WHERE
                        a.state not in ('canceled', 'expired')
                    GROUP BY
                        t.id
                    HAVING
                        t.project_id = $1
                        AND (
                            count(a.id) >= t.assignments_needed
                            OR t.canonical_result_id IS NOT NULL
                            )
